{"tid":1136820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粱君彥利用立法會法律顧問，就修訂逃犯條例要求保安局澄清","createTime":"2019-05-03T09:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T00:58:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"20395ef42d75f5e30cf538830003f5148f77bd44","tid":1136820,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>立法會秘書處 (法律事務部)</strong><br />\n法律事務部負責就法案及附屬法例擬備法律報告，並就與委員會議事程序有關的法律事宜，向立法會各個委員會提供意見。<span style=\"color: red;\">秘書處的法律顧問亦是立法機關的法律顧問，就與立法會議事程序有關的法律事宜，向立法會主席及立法會秘書提供意見。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據《基本法》第71條，立法會主席由議員互選產生。第六屆立法會主席的選舉於2016年10月12日，即新一屆立法會任期開始的首次會議上舉行，並<span style=\"color: red;\">由梁君彥議員當選為第六屆立法會主席</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>梁君彥:修訂逃犯條例直上大會未必可取</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2115623/%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%3A%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2115623%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5%253A%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%259B%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25BF%2585%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258F%2596&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjOxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=57be6011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2115623/%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%3A%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%96</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【逃犯條例】法案具爭議 梁君彥：引《議事規則》91條未必可取</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/320370/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%E5%85%B7%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5-%E5%BC%95-%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87-91%E6%A2%9D%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F320370%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%2585%25B7%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5-%25E5%25BC%2595-%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%2589%2587-91%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25BF%2585%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258F%2596&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjOxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=b3863059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/320370/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%E5%85%B7%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5-%E5%BC%95-%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87-91%E6%A2%9D%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%96</a><br />\n<br />\n梁君彥有陰謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c948ee9203aee33c2a43b29e0489143cba434884","tid":1136820,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:31:14.000Z","msg":"立法會法律顧問去信保安局，就修訂《逃犯條例》提出多項質疑，要求政府澄清。<br />\n<br />\n立法會法律顧問在信件指出，回歸前訂立的《逃犯條例》刪減了「中華人民共和國」字眼，條例立法原意是將內地排除在外，就內地與香港之間的逃犯移交，會在隨後階段透過另一個正式的引渡協議落實，法律顧問要求政府澄清是否及為何會改變做法。行政當局1997年亦曾表示，香港與廣東正商討移交逃犯安排，會由另一個法例處理。<br />\n<br />\n法律顧問又說，保安局在1998年曾經表示，香港與內地的逃犯引渡安排，會符合5項指導原則，包括一國兩制、兩地在法律與司法制度的差異等，要求政府澄清，有關原則在修訂《逃犯條例》草案是否仍適用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455812-20190503.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455812-20190503.htm&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjOxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=06628fe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455812-20190503.htm&h=d7463410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455812-20190503.htm</a>"},{"pid":"955efd5035bd69d41135eb42de5bfa264c867e0f","tid":1136820,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d0f5ce22cba3fad3953ee3f0e575e45ad79da9","tid":1136820,"uid":6604,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"商家佬自己都驚啦<br />\n何況 Andrew 佢自己都係 last-minute 先放棄 BC <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1eef6ad0a46096e2ab099a6b67f9a7b563ff3d6","tid":1136820,"uid":17510,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"20395ef42d75f5e30cf538830003f5148f77bd44","tid":1136820,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>立法會秘書處 (法律事務部)</strong><br />\n法律事務部負責就法案及附屬法例擬備法律報告，並就與委員會議事程序有關的法律事宜，向立法會各個委員會提供意見。<span style=\"color: red;\">秘書處的法律顧問亦是立法機關的法律顧問，就與立法會議事程序有關的法律事宜，向立法會主席及立法會秘書提供意見。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據《基本法》第71條，立法會主席由議員互選產生。第六屆立法會主席的選舉於2016年10月12日，即新一屆立法會任期開始的首次會議上舉行，並<span style=\"color: red;\">由梁君彥議員當選為第六屆立法會主席</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>梁君彥:修訂逃犯條例直上大會未必可取</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2115623/%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%3A%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2115623%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5%253A%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%259B%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%25